    <item>
      <title>sdhizumi at M8 Fest -Live Mix-</title>
      <link>https://sdhizumi.com/works/sdhizumiatm8festlivemix/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 27 Oct 2024 00:00:00 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>https://sdhizumi.com/works/sdhizumiatm8festlivemix/</guid>
      <description>[RELEASE] M3-2024 Autumn - &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://sdhizumi.com/img/works/sdhizumiatm8festlivemix.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;M8 Fest was held on 2024/09/07 at Circus Tokyo. I was really enjoyed this gig.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;This album has Live Mix that I performed on M8 Fest (rerecording) with unmixed versions each others.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I used 2 units of M8Tracker for that gig but 1 unit is made by myself that based on M8Headless. You can see on the album cover. I called this by H4NDM4T3.&lt;br&gt;&#xA;This unit is very memorable as my own memory of this event.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
